          <h2 class="section-title">Using AI with Intention.</h2>
          <p>
            One of the main goals of this portfolio is to show that using AI effectively is not just about generating content quickly.
            It involves defining the task clearly, writing useful prompts, evaluating the response, revising the output, and deciding
            where human judgment remains essential.
          </p>
          <p>
            Across these assignments, I aimed to explore not only what AI can produce, but also how it can support thinking,
            communication, and problem-solving in the AEC context.
          </p>
          <ul class="story-points">
            <li><strong>Prompt quality matters:</strong> better prompts led to more useful and more targeted outputs.</li>
            <li><strong>Review matters:</strong> AI-generated results still required interpretation, editing, and judgment.</li>
            <li><strong>Application matters:</strong> the most valuable uses were the ones tied to real tasks and real decisions.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

